  "label": "The Reliquary Stockroom",
  "description": "The Reliquary Stockroom occupies a low, ferrocrete chamber behind blast-rated internal shutters, built for rapid sealing within Pale Meridian Enclave’s siege architecture. Ration-tin crates, pressure-clamped cases, and waxed preservative casks stack in regimented bays beneath cog-stamped inventory plaques. Recessed lumen strips in the ribbed ceiling cast a flat, clinical light over scuffed deck plates and stenciled load lines. The air holds machine oil, preservative salts, and dry paper dust, reinforcing the tradehouse’s locked, audited circulation of goods.",
